description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELED. Experience stylish loft-style living in this 2 bedroom, 1 bath condo in Boston’s historic Fort Point neighborhood. A welcoming entrance, high ceilings, exposed brick and an open-concept layout blend industrial character with modern comfort. Large windows flood the space with natural light, highlighting the warmth of the brick and open floor plan. The kitchen offers modern finishes and ample storage, ideal for daily living and entertaining. Arched brick inlays provide charming niches for books and art. The spacious and bright primary bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet and large window. The second bedroom offers flexibility—ideal for guests, a home office or gym. In-unit laundry, great storage and a deeded outdoor parking space complete this unique offering. Enjoy vibrant city living just steps from the Seaport’s renowned dining, shopping and cultural destinations with convenient access to major commuter routes.
